title: "LLM Evaluation Toolkit"
message: "If you use this project, please cite it as below."
type: software

authors:
  - family-names: Taratuta
    given-names: Ekaterina

repository-code: https://github.com/LLM-Measurement-Lab/llm-evaluation-toolkit

abstract: >
  A small research-oriented toolkit for studying reliability and
  robustness of automated LLM evaluation pipelines, including tools
  for evaluator agreement analysis, adversarial evaluation behavior,
  and calibration of LLM-based judges.

